316
00:18:45.528 --> 00:18:48.758
And so that's why what we had to do is figure out how to create the

317
00:18:48.828 --> 00:18:52.808
durability. And by durability, what we did was we basically, by

318
00:18:52.848 --> 00:18:56.788
adding a targeting arm, we get much, much deeper desialylation

319
00:18:56.948 --> 00:19:00.908
and more durability, and we can keep it below this threshold of

