00:44:17.252 --> 00:44:17.592
setting.

726
00:44:19.112 --> 00:44:21.602
So at Triana, we asked the following question:

727
00:44:22.512 --> 00:44:26.412
Can a molecular glue degrader of ALK fusion proteins provide

728
00:44:26.472 --> 00:44:30.432
an orthogonal approach to treat ALK-positive non-small

729
00:44:30.492 --> 00:44:31.552
