00:44:52.652 --> 00:44:56.612
we took a proximity approach where

737
00:44:56.652 --> 00:44:57.392
we took

738
00:44:58.371 --> 00:44:59.852
ALK kinase domain

739
00:45:00.852 --> 00:45:04.262
and our proprietary cereblon library, and using a

