1090
01:05:32.604 --> 01:05:35.024
To expand upon this therapeutic index-

1091
01:05:36.904 --> 01:05:38.163
I'm too short, so...

1092
01:05:39.504 --> 01:05:39.844
Okay.

1093
01:05:40.884 --> 01:05:44.744
To expand upon this therapeutic index, targeted therapies have

1094
01:05:44.784 --> 01:05:48.624
been pursued with the expectation that if we can

1095
01:05:48.644 --> 01:05:52.604
direct our drug to the tissue of interest, we can reduce

1096
01:05:52.644 --> 01:05:55.124
the amount that is required to drive efficacy,

1097
01:05:56.104 --> 01:06:00.004
and by limiting off-target interactions, we can improve our

1098
01:06:00.024 --> 01:06:00.924
safety profile.

1099
01:06:02.304 --> 01:06:05.384
But these therapeutics have their own challenges.

1100
01:06:07.664 --> 01:06:10.844
For example, if we take a closer look at antibody drug conjugates,

1101
01:06:11.624 --> 01:06:15.004
traditionally, these have been generated by using either

1102
01:06:15.084 --> 01:06:18.104
