1116
01:07:04.844 --> 01:07:07.864
And for us, we are using a non-natural amino acid

1117
01:07:07.944 --> 01:07:11.748
platform.All of these technologies afford

1118
01:07:11.788 --> 01:07:13.448
us precision engineering,

1119
01:07:14.348 --> 01:07:18.088
precise control over conjugation site, precise

1120
01:07:18.208 --> 01:07:21.318
control over the number of drugs that are attached,

1121
01:07:22.228 --> 01:07:25.548
precise control over stability of our conjugates.

1122
01:07:26.728 --> 01:07:30.568
And as an added bonus, they are orthogonal chemistries.

1123
01:07:30.648 --> 01:07:34.548
They allow us to attach not one, but two drugs to the same

1124
01:07:34.608 --> 01:07:35.147
