1125
01:07:36.968 --> 01:07:40.828
Now, the advantages of dual payload ADCs, the list is as long

1126
01:07:40.848 --> 01:07:44.148
as my arm, but they've only given me 15 minutes.

1127
01:07:44.708 --> 01:07:46.868
So I've shortlisted a few of my favorites.

1128
01:07:47.428 --> 01:07:51.168
For starters, they allow us to address heterogeneous tumors.

1129
01:07:52.238 --> 01:07:55.528
They allow us to overcome mechanisms of drug resistance.

1130
01:07:56.288 --> 01:08:00.008
And ultimately, they allow us to drive more robust tumor regression.

1131
01:08:02.488 --> 01:08:05.988
CD30 is a target that is amenable to these approaches.

1132
01:08:06.728 --> 01:08:08.648
As a single-pass transmembrane protein

1133
01:08:09.508 --> 01:08:13.408
