01:08:16.168 --> 01:08:19.688
And it's a robust internalizer, which is desirable for antibody drug

1136
01:08:19.768 --> 01:08:20.329
conjugates.

1137
01:08:21.628 --> 01:08:22.108
Furthermore,

1138
01:08:23.228 --> 01:08:27.208
it is highly overexpressed in a number of cell types across

1139
01:08:27.268 --> 01:08:30.708
both Hodgkin and anaplastic large cell lymphomas, and

1140
01:08:31.508 --> 01:08:35.168
that expression profile is consistent throughout all stages of disease

1141
01:08:35.208 --> 01:08:35.748
progression.

1142
01:08:36.788 --> 01:08:38.949
The one caveat to CD30

1143
01:08:39.788 --> 01:08:43.468
is that there are several known mechanisms of drug

