1156
01:09:22.588 --> 01:09:22.949
However,

1157
01:09:24.489 --> 01:09:28.329
similar to other MMAE ADCs that have gone through the clinic,

1158
01:09:29.788 --> 01:09:33.348
unfortunately, it has had its limitations because of drug

1159
01:09:33.428 --> 01:09:34.748
