01:11:02.288 --> 01:11:04.408
Now, as far as the topo is concerned,

1183
01:11:05.568 --> 01:11:08.908
we wanted to make sure that we had a clinically relevant,

1184
01:11:09.468 --> 01:11:11.068
clinically validated dose,

1185
01:11:11.888 --> 01:11:15.528
and of course, there is always the matter of balancing our therapeutic index.

1186
01:11:16.028 --> 01:11:19.418
We want to drive robust tumor regression without compromising our

1187
01:11:19.508 --> 01:11:21.238
